   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. Theoretical Background: DARTS Algorithm"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.1 Problem Formulation\n",
    "\n",
    "NAS aims to automatically find optimal neural network architectures. DARTS formulates this as a bi-level optimization problem:\n",
    "\n",
    "**Architecture parameters (α)**: Learnable weights that determine which operations to use in each edge of the cell\n",
    "\n",
    "**Network weights (w)**: Standard weights of convolutional operations\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2.2 Mathematical Formulation\n",
    "\n",
    "The search space is a **cell** consisting of $B$ blocks. Each block connects two previous nodes:\n",
    "\n",
    "$$o_{(i,j)} = \\text{Softmax}(\\alpha_{(i,j)}) \\cdot \\text{op}_{k}(x_i)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "Where:\n",
    "- $\\alpha_{(i,j)}$ are the architecture parameters for edge $(i,j)$\n",
    "- $\\text{op}_{k}$ is one of $K$ candidate operations\n",
    "- $\\text{Softmax}$ normalizes operation weights\n",
    "\n",
    "### 2.3 Bi-level Optimization\n",
    "\n",
    "The key insight of DARTS is to optimize weights and architecture alternately:\n",
    "\n",
    "**Inner optimization (weights)**: $\\min_w L_{train}(w, \\alpha^*)$\n",
    "\n",
    "**Outer optimization (architecture)**: $\\min_\\alpha L_{val}(w^*, \\alpha)$\n",
    "\n",
    "where $w^*$ is obtained by:\n",
    "$$w^* = \\arg\\min_w L_{train}(w - \\xi \\nabla_w L_{train}(w, \\alpha), \\alpha)$$\n",
    "\n",
    "The gradient w.r.t. $\\alpha$ is approximated as:\n",
    "$$ \\nabla_\\alpha L_{val}(w^*, \\alpha) \\approx \\nabla_\\alpha L_{val}(w - \\xi \\nabla_w L_{train}(w, \\alpha), \\alpha) $$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### 2.4 Cell Architecture\n",
    "\n",
    "Each cell has:\n",
    "- **Normal cell**: Preserves spatial resolution\n",
    "- **Reduction cell**: Downsamples by 2x at 1/3 and 2/3 of depth"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
